reviewText:
Not much of a "collection." The three discs each only include three full episodes (so 9 mini episodes per disc). My son is happy so that makes it worth the $20 but there are larger, real collections of this show available for the same price elsewhere.  Definitely do NOT pay the $60+ it's listed at right now, that is beyond ridiculous! It does come in both English and French and is brand new/factory sealed.

No issues with the seller. Item was delayed in shipping and I was given the option of cancelling when they discovered this, which I appreciated and declined since there was no rush.
